\c 152 

\s NIWOWE BUHUNGIRO BWANJYE
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Ni\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd wowe Buhungiro bwanjye Mwami, ni\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd wowe Mahoro yanjye. Igihe ngeze aho nanirirwa, ni\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd wowe usubizamwo imbaraga.\bd*
\pc \bdit Mwami wanjye ndakwiringiye, kuko nziko udakoza isoni. Unshoboze ngukiranukire, kugezaho Uzagarukira.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Ni\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd wowe ubwawe wivugiye, ut\bd*\bd ’\bd*\bd abarushe n\bd*\bd ’\bd*\bd abaremerewe nimusange ndabaruhura, none nduhura imitwaro yanjye.\bd*
\pc \bdit Mwami wanjye ndakwiringiye, kuko nziko udakoza isoni. Unshoboze ngukiranukire, kugezaho Uzagarukira.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Ariko uwakwizeye Mukiza, akagushiraho ivyiringiro, Ijambo ryawe uhora uryibuka, kandi Usohoza ivyo wavuze Yesu.\bd*
\pc \bdit Mwami wanjye ndakwiringiye, kuko nziko udakoza isoni. Unshoboze ngukiranukire, kugezaho Uzagarukira.\bdit*
